{
  "stem": "4226.4",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And actually, it caused more panic amongst the Germans than, than the effective-- the Americans never, never looked down on the BMW.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They were throwing the bombs in the fog.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Half of them missed.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Half of them hit.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] And whatever they wanted to hit got hit.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "The fog was, was very depressing for, for, for, for the people, really.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I don't know why they did it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] They-- so we, we came to that camp, and we were put into barracks with triple-- we didn't have rooms.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "The whole barrack was one.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "We were about maybe [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] 200 in each.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I was still with my father.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And they organized working groups the next day.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And I was in a group with my father.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "We would stick together. 50 to go the other side-- through BMW, we were driven into a small camp erected for foremen, German foremen, and our-- whatever staff from BMW who were living there.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And they had-- we had to [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] clean potatoes for the kitchen.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And we, we built some barracks there, and even made-- we made-- before the  winter set in, we, we made walkways to each barrack made of piling, about a foot or two aboveground on little posts.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "So when snow comes, you can brush the snow off between the pilings and walk dry to each barrack between the washroom and the barrack, and the dining room, and the kitchen to the barracks.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And the barracks were all spread in, in bush setting, painted dark green.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And part were occupied by night shift.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "The-- those people were sleeping.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And you couldn't-- not to be disturbed.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "My father had the potato shellers, 10 boys and, and him in the kitchen there-- or outside the kitchen.",
      "word_count": 19
    }
  ],
